uot;China undoubtedly represents one of our principal partners and one cannot forget that is is now an essential actor to address any international scenario,&quot; Di Maio said at a joint press conference with Wang.<br />\n<br />\nWith China, the Italian foreign minister said, &quot;there is an exchange founded on frankness&quot;.<br />\nHe said &quot;our international position is very clear to all, starting with our membership of NATO which is stronger than ever. &quot;This enables us to have a healthy and fair relationship with China&quot;.//"},{"pid":"d2fd41c9f8b9156da784dc72c6fd720a504a0232","tid":2174132,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T16:55:39.000Z","msg":"奶啊奶啊奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f698a2f2e42106a0876f5121928fce18a9302b3","tid":2174132,"uid":189564,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T16:58:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pogyGHw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpogyGHw.jpg&h=f04ec448&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec94eba270010f6b4bd8b530f47d901b055d1c2c","tid":2174132,"uid":89160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T16:58:59.000Z","msg":"google translate:<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">Dangerous crossings from Di Maio</span></strong><br />\nChinese minister Wang Yi begins a European tour from Rome to defend interests on 5G (on which the government chooses to wait) and beyond. The foreign-wanted activist Nathan Law, who carries the flag of Hong Kong, now lowered by Beijing, will also be waiting for him<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.huffingtonpost.it/entry/incroci-pericolosi-per-di-maio_it_5f449ed5c5b66a80ee172147\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffingtonpost.it%2Fentry%2Fincroci-pericolosi-per-di-maio_it_5f449ed5c5b66a80ee172147&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=e7096051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.huffingtonpost.it/entry/incroci-pericolosi-per-di-maio_it_5f449ed5c5b66a80ee172147</a>"},{"pid":"0cac53d12455ae300121a1f31ad71be756da70ea","tid":2174132,"uid":197213,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T17:00:32.000Z","msg":"我覺得自己好靚仔，葉子楣亦都好賢良淑德，陳百祥係世界上最叻嘅人，袁木好誠實，李鵬係我哋最偉大嘅領袖！"},{"pid":"37a2e773d4495b2f1bd7fbd10a5ec19fccc0d19a","tid":2174132,"uid":89160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T17:02:33.000Z","msg":"google translate: <br />\n// &quot;There are those who want to damage EU-China relations &quot; Relations between China and the EU &quot;suffer from provocation and damage from external forces&quot;. In this context &quot;my visit serves to consolidate relations between China and the EU&quot; added the Chinese Foreign Minister. &quot;A united, stable and prosperous Europe is important for the whole world: this is our strategic judgment. China will continue to support European integration with its concrete actions&quot;//<br />\n<br />\nSee more at: <a href=\"http://www.rainews.it/dl/rainews/articoli/Di-Maio-incontra-il-ministro-degli-Esteri-cinese-Wang-preservare-indipendenza-Hong-Kong-56a3b8ef-9ddd-4c36-a681-6b0f78f32169.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rainews.it%2Fdl%2Frainews%2Farticoli%2FDi-Maio-incontra-il-ministro-degli-Esteri-cinese-Wang-preservare-indipendenza-Hong-Kong-56a3b8ef-9ddd-4c36-a681-6b0f78f32169.html&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=e3634277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rainews.it/dl/rainews/articoli/Di-Maio-incontra-il-ministro-degli-Esteri-cinese-Wang-preservare-indipendenza-Hong-Kong-56a3b8ef-9ddd-4c36-a681-6b0f78f32169.html</a>"},{"pid":"9b0b8c93252d7731b6c918a63bbc1a7fecad4461","tid":2174132,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T17:03:00.000Z","msg":"如果義大利保持中立，我們要用1個師防守義大利<br />\n如果義大利加入敵方，我們要用3個師防守義大利<br />\n如果義大利加入我方&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"7c0aeeece773e7da900c921b63b0550dc1a5b744","tid":2174132,"uid":276662,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T17:04:37.000Z","msg":"死左咁多人都要奶 真係唔明個腦點樣諗"},{"pid":"ab664a14842243e12a32c5c745e0447781f3389e","tid":2174132,"uid":223664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T17:06:27.000Z","msg":"真係唔識醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8faab258a8b55eb34a2b011389f5ff5cd9025082","tid":2174132,"uid":16057,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T17:12:09.000Z","msg":"根據翻兩次世界大戰 意大利站係咁樣既一邊 一啲都唔出奇"},{"pid":"cfae8f83e857f4725a0aaadf4448fe0c10db4728","tid":2174132,"uid":89160,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T17:12:16.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"orange\">睇中文既歐洲新聞，推薦大家睇《歐洲動態》：</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://europechinese.blogspot.com/2020/08/madama.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feuropechinese.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F08%2Fmadama.html&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDhphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=1f4a79cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://europechinese.blogspot.com/2020/08/madama.html</a><br />\n<br />\n迪馬約：意中是夥伴、北約是盟友<br />\n<br />\n//迪馬約在記者會上，正式表達了意大利的香港問題立場，正好反映上述基調。這個說法，較德國和法國偏弱，但以意大利的角度來說，算是強硬。基本上就是：意大利無興趣就香港問題高調採取行動或表態，但亦不會作出支持中國、鬆動歐盟立場的態度。//<br />\n<br />\n//最明顯的是：根據意大利政府數據，在今年1-6月，意大利對中國出口按年大跌18.6%&mdash;&mdash;這可以以疫情擾亂全球貿易來解釋，但從中國進口同期卻不跌反升，較去年同期增長1.3%，主要是因為意大利從中國進口大量醫療用品。這令一些意大利人覺得「被搵笨」，一帶一路無用，中國疫情送暖只是用來刺激自己出口。//<br />\n<br />\n//最後一提：王毅拜訪迪馬約、以及會後記者會的地點，安排在Villa Madama，而非羅冠聰今天在外面示威及見記者的外交部大樓。Villa Madama是地位較高的接待外賓地點，政府領袖或元首到訪，通常來這裏，但不少外長會面也曾安排在這兒，以示尊重。//"},{"pid":"26c41da36e06094698bbb810a18a0cb68a0bc3f5","tid":2174132,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T17:17:19.000Z","msg":"古羅馬就勁<br />\n而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3035ca80d4c191ea3fa59bd7b121ccf